short_description: Cemetary
description: |
  This is the Keep's cemetary. There are dozens of burial plots,
  some still covered by freshly turned earth. To the north you
  see the southern flank of the inn. A small balcony on its 
  upper story looks down upon the cemetary. An enormous oak
  occupies the center of the graveyard and the ground is littered
  with branches.
